title: Liberty League Auxiliaries Unbanned
subtitle: The judges have re-legalized the Liberty League auxiliaries.
view-if: sh_banned == 1 and sh_ban_timer == 0 and judicial_reform < 2
on-arrival: sh_banned = 0; sh_strength += 100; sh_militancy += 0.01
tags: event

Judges have ordered the Liberty League auxiliaries to be re-legalized. They immediately return to mass recruiting.
